{"word":"ἐπιτρίβω","slug":"ἐπιτρίβω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιτρίβω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἐπετρίβην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to rub on the surface, to crush</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be galled</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to afflict, distress, destroy, ruin</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; of an actor, <i>to murder</i> a character, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be utterly destroyed</i> or <i>undone</i>, <b>Solon.</b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>ἐπιτριβείης</el> <i>be hung!</i> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}